                              "name": "para1",
                              "fill": "#1F1F1F",
                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "content": "SwarmNote 是一个去中心化的实时协同编辑器，基于 CRDT (Conflict-free Replicated Data Types) 和 P2P 网络构建。本文档描述其核心架构设计。",
                              "lineHeight": 1.8,
                              "fontFamily": "Inter",
                              "fontSize": 15,
                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "aWwmq",
                              "name": "h2",
                              "fill": "#0A0A0A",
                              "content": "## 数据同步层",
                              "fontFamily": "Inter",
                              "fontSize": 22,
                              "fontWeight": "600"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "8owlX",
                              "name": "para2",
                              "fill": "#1F1F1F",
                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "content": "系统使用 Yjs 作为 CRDT 引擎，所有文档编辑操作被转化为 Y.Doc 的 update 包。这些 update 包通过 libp2p 的 GossipSub 协议在 P2P 网络中广播。",
                              "lineHeight": 1.8,
                              "fontFamily": "Inter",
                              "fontSize": 15,
                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "frame",
